    <text type="letter">
        <body>

            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="duk.00385.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1875-02-11">Feb 11<hi rend="superscript"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> 1875</date>
                </dateline>

            </opener>

            <p>I received your Postal Card Feb-5-1875</p>
            <p>But you have not <choice><sic>forgoten</sic><corr>forgotten</corr></choice> your <choice><sic>littel</sic><corr>little</corr></choice> Michigan friend yet&#8212;Well i have not <choice><sic>forgotton</sic><corr>forgotten</corr></choice> my Hospital Friend yet and I hope that I never will</p>
            <p>I read in the newspaper that you had been sick but I trust that you have got well again</p>
            <p>I had a shock of <choice><sic>Paralasis</sic><corr>paralysis</corr></choice> on the right side of my person I was <choice><sic>layed</sic><corr>laid</corr></choice> up three weeks you see I can not write as
            
            
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="duk.00385.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                I used <choice><sic>too</sic><corr>to</corr></choice> before I was afflicted. I am not <choice><sic>abel</sic><corr>able</corr></choice> to work on my farm and I have rented it for 5 years Well Walt I think I will go to <name type="place">California</name> next fall is <choice><sic>noth</sic><corr>nothing</corr></choice> <choice><sic>hapens</sic><corr>happens</corr></choice></p>
            
            <p>This is the first letter I have <choice><sic>writen</sic><corr>written</corr></choice> since this <choice><sic>accidence</sic><corr>accident</corr></choice> <choice><sic>hapand</sic><corr>happened</corr></choice></p>
            <p>I will <choice><sic>writ</sic><corr>write</corr></choice> better one next time</p>
            <p>Good <choice><sic>by</sic><corr>bye</corr></choice> God Bless my old acquaintance Walt Whitman</p>
            

            <closer>
                <salute>Yours Truly</salute>
                <signed><choice><sic>Ruben</sic><corr>Reuben</corr></choice> Farwell</signed>
           
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="duk.00385.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/> 
                
                <address>
                    <addrLine>address</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Nankin P.</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Wayne Co</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Michigan</addrLine>
                </address>
                
            </closer>
            
            <postscript>
                <p>You see that it bothers me some to make letters</p>
                <p>Excuse all <choice><sic>mistaks</sic><corr>mistakes</corr></choice></p>
            </postscript>
            
